net.uniform.impl

Class AbstractHTMLElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.uniform.impl.AbstractElement
      • net.uniform.impl.AbstractHTMLElement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Element
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Button, Checkbox, DatePicker, ElementWithOptions, Hidden, Input, Textarea

    public abstract class AbstractHTMLElement
extends AbstractElement
    Default HTML element implementation. Extends the abstract implementation in order to:
    • Automatically set the id as the id and name HTML attributes
    • Add filters for trimming and removing control characters from any input value
    Author:
    Eduardo Ramos
